              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium mr-2 mt-0.5">2</span>
                U.S. resident with valid Apple ID
